cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE 

This paper deals with machine translation and natural language processing, which are the primary focus areas of the sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves statistical approaches, which are commonly used in information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves the use of phonemes, which are related to speech recognition and natural language generation, which are covered in sub-categories cs.LG and cs.NE respectively.
